spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: RELEASE VERSION - MIL-STD-1553B is a 1 Mb/s command/response, dual-redundant, time-multiplexed serial data bus used in aircraft, spacecraft, military vehicles, and severe control environments. Core1553BRT provides a complete, MIL-STD-1553B Remote Terminal (RT), and is compatible with legacy remote terminal systems and supports standard off-chip 1553B transceivers.
